    <item>
      <title>保守党民意调查显示改革威胁，苏纳克向养老金领取者提供减税优惠</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/sunak-offers-pensioners-tax-cut-as-tory-poll-shows-reform-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果他的保守党打破胜局并赢得大选，总理里希·苏纳克将向养老金领取者承诺减税，这是试图支撑核心选票的最新策略，因为内部民意调查显示，由于保守党的复兴，保守党可能会失去 100 多个席位。右翼英国改革党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/sunak-offers-pensioners-tax-cut-as-tory-poll-shows-reform-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 21:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜火箭在飞行中爆炸，交易打击金正恩的卫星计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/n-korea-thought-to-have-attempted-satellite-launch-south-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜运载间谍卫星的火箭在升空后不久就爆炸了，这对领导人金正恩来说是一次挫折。金正恩去年前往俄罗斯寻求帮助，将一系列侦察探测器送入轨道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/n-korea-thought-to-have-attempted-satellite-launch-south-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 15:02:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列空袭、埃及卫兵死亡加剧紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/israel-egypt-troops-exchange-fire-in-gaza-says-israeli-media</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，一名埃及士兵在加沙边境口岸与以色列军队的冲突中丧生，进一步加剧了地区紧张局势，此前以色列空袭造成流离失所者营地中约 45 名巴勒斯坦人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/israel-egypt-troops-exchange-fire-in-gaza-says-israeli-media</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 13:55:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西央行行长罗伯托·坎波斯·内托表示通胀预测将会改善</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/brazil-analysts-see-faster-inflation-into-2026-as-outlook-dims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西央行行长表示，消费者价格预测将有所改善，此前一项受到密切关注的调查显示，经济学家将 2024-2026 年通胀预期上调至进一步高于目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/brazil-analysts-see-faster-inflation-into-2026-as-outlook-dims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:57:07 GMT</pubDate>
